node.text: Popping into @renhotels for a much needed holiday cocktail #sponsored. After spending the day shopping for holiday gifts I am ready to unwind and relax at this hidden holiday gem. #RenHotels #DiscoverThisWay #RenNavigator #RenEvenings #RenDesign
Flowers, food and friends what a wonderful way to spend the day @ilfioristanyc #prettycitynewyork

For our last stop on our adventure around NYC with @lincoln, we stopped over to @aireancientbaths_us in Tribeca for a relaxing soak and massage. #ad 
Wellness is one of the core concepts that inspired the all-new #LincolnAviator, and the available Perfect Position Front Seats with Active Motion Massage let you take that just left the spa feeling right on the road with you. I even got to keep one for the weekend! It truly is so quiet inside and such a calming drive - I'm going to miss this lovely luxury crossover.

Last week I took Team @lincoln to one of my favorite local Brooklyn spots, @cafe_colette #ad 
It was the perfect pitstop and lunch to fuel us up for our day trip in our fleet of Aviators. The greenhouse garden in the back is so beautifully designed and feels just like a little sanctuary away from the bustle of the city, just like the all-new #LincolnAviator. I had such a great time showing @ashleyklemieux a little slice of Brooklyn charm. Stay tuned this week for our next stop!

This week I played tourist in my own city with Team @lincoln making some new friends and adventuring around in the all-new #LincolnAviator #ad

We kicked off our rainy day with some coffee at @mrchotels Seaport - @krystal_bick matched perfectly with the Flight Blue model. Stay tuned for more highlights from my day trip with Lincoln this week!

So grateful to have had the opportunity to visit @rifflinhitchlodge. I’m a city person, born and raised but I could definitely appreciate the untouched wilderness of Labrador, Canada #🇨🇦🌊🌲🚁🎣What a treat to experience this part of the world. #rifflinhitchlodge

Thank you @rifflinhitchlodge and @xbecca for a once in a lifetime, unforgettable trip to the untouched wilderness of Northern Labrador, Canada. From the cozy accommodations, world class fishing, special meals celebrating local foods by @pinballchef Chris Chaisson to the wonderful staff that make you feel right at home, what a memorable experience. #rifflinhitchlodge

#ad I believe it is important to focus on eating balanced foods with natural ingredients. That is why it’s important to treat yourself to a cup of new rich & creamy Krímí skyr from @icelandicprovisions. On a scale of 1-10 creaminess, Krímí is an 11!!! Made with whole foods the way nature intended you to enjoy them. @icelandicprovisions curated combination of delicious ingredients like Strawberry Rhubarb and Mixed Berry means #MoreForMe while I am maintaining a healthy lifestyle #IcelandicProvisions
There is beauty everywhere in #sanmigueldeallende

A must see if you are in San Miguel de Allende, the Chapel 💒 of Jimmy Ray 
@AnadoGroove. Founded in 2012 as a vehicle to present the work of @anadogroove along with other artists the gallery is feast for the eyes! #sanmigueldeallende
